Tribhangi Dance Festival: In celebration of their 30th anniversary, the Tribhangi Dance Theatre is hosting a dance festival featuring 15 dance groups from various disciplines. Details: The festival is on until March 31 at the Market Theatre, 56 Margaret Mcingana Street, Newtown.
